  "title": "Infrastructure Engineer (Maintenance)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Configure, maintain, and upgrade servers, networks, and related systems</li><li>Perform asset management and maintain accurate records</li><li>Monitor infrastructure health and security on a daily basis</li><li>Troubleshoot infrastructure and network issues</li><li>Manage and document change management processes</li><li>Respond to incidents and service requests within SLA</li><li>Liaise with vendors and service providers</li><li>Automate tasks using Bash/PowerShell and scripting languages (e.g. Python, Perl)</li><li>Support infrastructure projects and ad-hoc tasks</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum 2 years of relevant experience (Engineer level)</li><li>Strong troubleshooting skills using log analysis and systematic problem tracing</li><li><strong>Servers:</strong> Windows Server, Red Hat</li><li><strong>Hypervisors:</strong> Hyper-V, VMware, Nutanix</li><li><strong>Networking:</strong> Cisco, Aruba, Dell, HPE</li><li><strong>Backup:</strong> NetBackup, Veeam, Cohesity</li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> Hitachi, Pure Storage, HPE, Dell EMC</li></ul><p><strong>Work Location:</strong> Tampines<br /></p><p>(EA Reg No: 20C0312)<br />Please email a copy of your detailed resume to <strong>qianyu@talentsis.com.sg</strong> for immediate processing.<br />Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>",
